prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style sloth wearing a party hat, hanging upside down from a lush, beautifully illustrated branch of tropical hibiscus flowers and monstera leaves. The sloth is smiling dreamily and holding a single, lit birthday candle with one of its toes. The entire scene is rendered in a detailed, 2D botanical illustration style with soft, organic shapes and a vibrant, natural color palette. Centered below the branch, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Let's get wild... slowly."
